9:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常都係暈，個世界慢，啲感官放大左幾倍，好撚肚餓<br />\n種類主要分三種：<br />\nRelax<br />\n亢奮<br />\n訓到仆街</blockquote><br />\n除左亢奮其他都好有用"},{"pid":"e7fcaebd68c1fdbb9d5529a65b7e0eb9f3281769","tid":483293,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T17:31:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勁暈 即刻行返屋企<br />\n條行人天橋好似波浪咁 企都企唔穩<br />\n完全唔係好似d戲咁 食完係咁笑 好過癮咁<br />\n個口勁乾 好似腫晒咁 個口冇晒知覺<br />\n清醒返之後記憶力差左勁多</blockquote><br />\n最後個句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0023008fc92d9d2a61077649889d03d89b080c","tid":483293,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T17:32:44.000Z","msg":"發夢有朋友叫我食 但個陣唔夠膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de890977cc1f7888e9df36a3cd5a76a5a238261","tid":483293,"uid":33154,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係話大麻嘅傷害同食煙參唔多，又唔會上癮，我都試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇你歲數<br />\n22歲後<br />\n你食大麻傷害一定低過煙<br />\n<br />\n但22歲前成日食<br />\n有機會對大腦造成傷害<br />\n記憶力會下降<br />\n<br />\n同埋weed呢d gateway drugs<br />\n會令你對drugs呢樣野既心理戒線降低<br />\n好容易會開始接觸埋其他野<br />\n自己睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打機對暴力接觸太大<br />\n心理界線降低<br />\n好易殺人放火<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係d假設理論</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢 d 戇鳩假設性理論有時睇到都唔知應唔應該笑。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你試過你就會明<br />\n<br />\n就以去澳洲WH為例<br />\n最易接觸到既就係草同冰<br />\n如果你未掂過草<br />\n有人問你試唔試冰<br />\n你緊係可以好堅決咁拒絕<br />\n<br />\n但如果你smoke過<br />\n嘗試過藥物影響大腦既滋味<br />\n同樣有人問你試唔試冰<br />\n你點都會有少少猶疑<br />\n<br />\n當然啦<br />\n我唔係話smoke過既人一定會掂埋其他野<br />\n好多人意志都好堅定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但相比冇smoke過既人<br />\n個機會率真係會大d<br />\n都係果句<br />\n自己睇路啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb2aecf222c93371ed1388b80f4e1ac391695b7","tid":483293,"uid":126958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T17:59:32.000Z","msg":"真係好chill?,唔係港女個種chill<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  頭輕 吸幾下個肚好快脹 但係5-10min之後個肚好似乜都冇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb19fec2c559a6e9dc7ef10d46700309fc19f7a5","tid":483293,"uid":12980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T18:30:23.000Z","msg":"琴晚先係Nevada 食完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba9293e84730b3582e86b15a225fcc25f7b70a6","tid":483293,"uid":12980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T18:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>琴晚先係Nevada 食完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食完好想笑<br />\n少少野都會笑唔停<br />\n除左笑同口乾啦<br />\n用bong 食"},{"pid":"5bd8f316b78e8916d0f4f6a0f7fe8a8f64193cdb","tid":483293,"uid":99582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T18:40:40.000Z","msg":"我試過食完會好驚 好似驚恐症咁 要即刻返屋企 沖涼訓覺 <br />\n<br />\n跟住心跳得勁快 一合埋眼訓就係咁轉轉轉 成兩個鐘先散<br />\n<br />\n成身無力 好似想瀨尿咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但另一次就好舒服 好好訓 無咩不良反應"},{"pid":"24ecf5c2d6f8e6504b461ad0c125dcbcda1f65e8","tid":483293,"uid":6106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T18:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係Amsterdam食過space cake <br />\n心跳去到光速 成晚都唔舒服<br />\n好撚恐怖 控制唔到</blockquote><br />\n加一"},{"pid":"547feefb01e34cab3a847c5c2baa989e2ba50fac","ti